    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309950/extras/ddb3c87bfc7f3157eacaac8e4e268257.poster.avif?t=1745814512\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309950/extras/ddb3c87bfc7f3157eacaac8e4e268257.webm?t=1745814512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309950/extras/ddb3c87bfc7f3157eacaac8e4e268257.mp4?t=1745814512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>一名怒火中烧的女孩单枪匹马挑战邪教，用一发又一发子弹将邪教徒逐个击破，直到揪出她真正的目标：邪教头目。一路上她将揭开这个神秘教团的黑暗真相，了解他们以主人的名义犯下的滔天罪行。<br><br>在这款第三人称战术解谜射击游戏中，你将操控一发子弹，引导它穿过难度和复杂程度越来越高的关卡以击杀邪教徒、触发陷阱以及重塑环境。每发子弹都不能浪费，精准命中将得到回报。消灭邪教的体验极佳，花式击杀更是爽快度拉满。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309950/extras/039d1646f77c8dae594aecb17a47e088.poster.avif?t=1745814512\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309950/extras/039d1646f77c8dae594aecb17a47e088.webm?t=1745814512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309950/extras/039d1646f77c8dae594aecb17a47e088.mp4?t=1745814512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一发子弹灭众敌</h2>《Children of the Sun》集战术狙击、解谜与轻度潜行要素于一身，呈现独一无二的第三人称射击游戏体验。每关你只有一发子弹，但你可以进行在命中时重新瞄准、绕过障碍物、加速击穿护甲等操作，让这关键的一发子弹大放异彩。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309950/extras/0c1362968a136909b5375fd9f87d5938.poster.avif?t=1745814512\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309950/extras/0c1362968a136909b5375fd9f87d5938.webm?t=1745814512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309950/extras/0c1362968a136909b5375fd9f87d5938.mp4?t=1745814512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >仪式献祭</h2>沉浸在这个黑暗扭曲的复仇故事中，猎杀恶名昭彰的邪教。《Children of the Sun》不仅有一弹歼敌的独特动作要素，还有引人入胜、充满谜团的故事线。在你向毁掉你生活的邪教复仇并追杀神秘的头目的过程中，真相也会逐渐水落石出。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309950/extras/1339ce06599615b87dca5e3f99bab11a.poster.avif?t=1745814512\" width=600 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309950/extras/1339ce06599615b87dca5e3f99bab11a.webm?t=1745814512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1309950/extras/1339ce06599615b87dca5e3f99bab11a.mp4?t=1745814512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >杀戮不止</h2>可重复游玩是《Children of the Sun》的设计理念之一。每一关都有多种解决方案，鼓励玩家发挥创造力，不断试错。游戏拥有令人满意的得分系统，精准与高效均可得到分数奖励。之后你还能查看在线排行榜，看看自己与好友以及全世界玩家相比水平如何。",
